: 298}, {\"ngram\": \"staffers\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"editorial\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But list columns and pieces remain forever popular, from power rankings to mock drafts to predictions.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"list columns\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"power rankings\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"mock drafts\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"predictions\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement The latter is why I am here.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not done many prediction columns in this space since joiningThe Athletic, but I thought it would be interesting at the beginning of 2024 to offer some thoughts on what will happen this year insports media.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many prediction columns\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"this space\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"joiningThe Athletic\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"some thoughts\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"insports media\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Check back in December to see how I did.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox CEO Lachlan Murdoch announced in May 2022 that Brady had agreed to joinFox Sportsas its lead NFL analyst when he retired from the NFL.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"score\": 