nd of the 2024-25 season.\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3999, \"end\": 4002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_on_CBS\", \"score\": 0.9997331463196725, \"rank\": 0.000266876063745096, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_on_CBS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_on_CBS\"}, {\"begin\": 4028, \"end\": 4032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.719267516666483e-32, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 4037, \"end\": 4043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4587222870865427e-13, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\"}, {\"begin\": 4049, \"end\": 4058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.149059466185489e-31, \"text\": \"Discovery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4077}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024-25 season\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By that time, the league will have been paid a combined $24 billion for the contracts.\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"the league\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4125}, {\"ngram\": \"the contracts\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like most people who write about this stuff, I believe everything sets up for the NBA to add media p